  "instructions": [
    "Heat ghee in a pan over medium heat, then add onions and cook until golden brown.",
    "Add ginger, garlic, and spices, cook for 1 minute.",
    "Add tomatoes and cook for 5 minutes.",
    "Add beef shin and cook until browned on all sides.",
    "Add beef shin broth and bring to a boil.",
    "Add rice and stir to coat with broth, then transfer to a layering dish.",
    "Soak kombu in water for 30 minutes, then drain and discard water.",
    "Add soaked kombu to the layering dish and layer with rice and beef shin, finishing with a layer of rice on top.",
    "Cover with foil and bake at 180°C for 45 minutes, then remove foil and continue baking for 15 minutes.",
    "Let rest for 10 minutes before serving."
